In this section you create NSX Edge Transport Nodes. The Transport Node is what allow Edge Node to exchange traffic for Virtual Networks among other NSX Nodes.

	* Add both `tz-vlan` and `tz-overlay` NSX Transport Zones to the NSX Edge Transport Nodes. Controller Connectivity and Manager Connectivity should be **UP**.
	* Refer to the MAC addresses of the Edge VM interfaces you deployed to deploy your virtual NSX Edges:
  		* Connect the `hs-overlay` N-VDS to the vNIC (`fp-eth#`) that matches the MAC address of the second NIC from your deployed Edge VM.
  		* Connect the `hs-vlan` N-VDS to the vNIC (`fp-eth#`) that matches the MAC address of the third NIC from your deployed Edge VM.

